title: 1.14- The Humble Petition and Advice
itunes:title: 1.14- The Humble Petition and Advice
description: The dissolution of the First Protectorate Parliament led to the brief and unpopular Rule of the Major Generals. When the Second Protectorate Parliament was finally called they tried to make Oliver Cromwell king.
